{
  "texts": [
    "This framework was designed to predict teams' performance early and demonstrated superior performance compared to traditional methods [33].",
    "It was specifically tailored to handle two-category classification tasks.",
    "Wang and colleagues presented AS-SAN, Adaptive Sparse Self-Attention Network, which predicts the fine-grained performance of students in online courses [8].",
    "Karimi et al.",
    "constructed a knowledge map using the DOPE, the Deep Online Performance Evaluation method."
  ]
}